# EaseElite â€“ Travel & Package Assistance Platform

EaseElite is a web-based platform that simplifies air travel by connecting Travellers, Companions, Carriers, and Package Senders. The platform ensures safe, cost-effective, and guided travel experiences.

## Key Features
- Connect first-time travellers with companions
- Send and receive packages through verified carriers
- KYC verification for user authentication
- AI-based pairing for travellers and service providers
- Secure payment system for transactions
- Feedback and rating system for service quality
- Real-time updates and notifications

## Roles & Actions

### 1. Admin
- Manage user accounts, disputes, and compliance
- Provide support and communicate important updates
- Collaborate with technical teams for smooth operations

### 2. Companion
- Create profile, complete KYC, select plan
- Share itinerary and tickets
- Meet travellers at the airport and assist
- Provide feedback post travel

### 3. First-Time Traveller
- Create profile and complete KYC
- Share travel details and ID
- Paired with companion using AI
- Travel with companion and provide feedback

### 4. Carrier
- Upload travel and ID details
- Receive sender requests and finalize package offers
- Transport packages to recipients safely

### 5. Package Sender
- Upload ID and package details
- Select best AI-suggested carrier
- Pay based on volume and weight
- Track package delivery status

## Tech Stack
- Backend: ASP.NET MVC, Web API, SQL Server
- Frontend: Angular, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap
- Database: SQL Server with stored procedures
- Features: KYC verification, Payment gateway
